Monadic devas are a kind of Deva tasked to protect the interests of Good in the Inner Planes. They have dark brown skin, jet hair, and green eyes. They can pass into any Inner Plane at will with no ill effect. 

      Sources:&nbsp;
    
            
                    Planescape Monstrous Compendium Appendix One        
              
                    Fiend Folio (D&amp;D 3.5)